### Login as the seeded single-role buyer
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "buyer",
  "password": "Buyer#123"
}

### Login as the seeded MULTI-role user (Buyer + Seller)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "multi",
  "password": "Multi#123"
}

### Wrong password (should fail with 401)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "buyer",
  "password": "wrong-password"
}

### Profile WITH a token (should succeed)
GET http://localhost:3000/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJjbXF2dGI2M3IwMDA4OHdtYnZyNjljdm5sIiwidXNlcm5hbWUiOiJidXllciIsInJvbGVzIjpbIkJVWUVSIl0sImFjdGl2ZVJvbGUiOiJCVVlFUiIsInRva2VuVmVyc2lvbiI6MCwiaWF0IjoxNzgyNTM3NzE3LCJleHAiOjE3ODI1Mzg2MTd9.EkmK3Z4cpghgDVFo7KxQppmFz0GWHhuhiCMN3HLoCVM

